<subSubSection pageId="48" pageNumber="49" type="discussion">
<paragraph blockId="48.[151,1436,426,783]" pageId="48" pageNumber="49">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,315,722,747]" pageId="48" pageNumber="49">Remarks.</emphasis>
This deep-water species displays sexual dimorphism, where females have evolved a deep and elongated apical disc to brood the young; males having a monobasal apical disc.
</paragraph>
